@startuml Prompts_Approver_Flow
!theme mimeograph
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/VladimirMrCarrot/mrcarrot13666.puml/refs/heads/main/puml_theme.puml

title Prompts Approver — Process Flow v4.0

actor User as U
participant "Prompts Approver\n(AI)" as AI
database "starter.md\n(Persistent Memory)" as MD
database "Perplexity\nAccount Memory" as PM

== Step 1: Input ==
U -> AI : Draft prompt\n(+ tool name, optional)

== Step 2: Tool Check ==
opt Tool NOT specified
    AI -> U : Which tool is this for?
    U -> AI : Provides tool name
end

== Step 3: Understanding & Format Check ==
AI -> U : My understanding of the task: [rephrase]\n──────────────────────\nOutput format — confirm or correct:\n- Prompt language: EN (fixed)\n- Result language: UA / EN / Bilingual?\n- Detail level: detailed / medium / minimal?\n- Structure: sections / bullets / text / tables?\n- Tone: technical / accessible / academic?\n- Anything to include or avoid?

opt User says NOT OK
    U -> AI : Provides corrections
    AI -> U : Rephrased understanding + updated format
    U -> AI : OK
end

== Step 4: Tool Analysis ==
opt Tool is NOT optimal
    AI -> U : Suggest alternative(s) + explanation why
    U -> AI : Accept or reject

    alt User ACCEPTS alternative
        AI -> AI : Use suggested tool
    else User REJECTS
        AI -> AI : Use user's original tool
    end
end

== Step 5-6: Prompt Generation & Delivery ==
AI -> AI : Craft optimized prompt (EN)\n+ embed result language instruction
AI -> U : Optimized prompt (EN)\n+ Explanation (EN + UA)

== Step 7: Confirmation ==
U -> AI : OK / feedback

== Step 8: Edit Check ==
AI -> U : Any edits or workflow improvements?

alt User HAS improvements
    U -> AI : Provides changes
    AI -> AI : Update internal algorithm

    == Step 9-10: Sync Persistent Memory ==
    AI -> MD : Update starter.md\n(version + date + changes)
    AI -> PM : Save to Account Memory
    MD --> AI : Saved
    PM --> AI : Saved
    AI -> U : Algorithm vX.X updated\nstarter.md + Account Memory synced
else No improvements
    AI -> U : Process complete
end

note over MD, PM
  Conflict resolution:
  Account Memory > starter.md
  Always use newer version
end note

@enduml